<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container mt-3 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Non-Profit Initiatives</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        At Boomerang, we believe in the power of collective goodwill to spark
        meaningful change. Whether you're advancing education, supporting
        community development, or driving social impact, Boomerang provides the
        platform to bring your vision to life.
    </p>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h3>Your Cause, Our Support</h3>
            <p>
                We empower individuals and organizations to raise funds for
                causes that matter. With flexible funding options tailored for
                non-profit endeavors, you can focus on making a difference
                without the constraints of all-or-nothing goals.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1732147145548-0c245396a268?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxmZWF0dXJlZC1waG90b3MtZmVlZHwyMnx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
                alt="Non-Profit Cause"
                class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
            <h3>Engage and Inspire</h3>
            <p>
                Share your mission with a community that cares. Craft a
                compelling narrative, outline your objectives, and connect with
                backers who are passionate about making a positive impact. Your
                story has the power to inspire action.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1732147145548-0c245396a268?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxmZWF0dXJlZC1waG90b3MtZmVlZHwyMnx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
                alt="Engage and Inspire"
                class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h3>Transparency Builds Trust</h3>
            <p>
                Honesty is the cornerstone of successful fundraising. Clearly
                communicate how the funds will be used and the difference they
                will make. Our platform fosters trust between organizers and
                supporters, ensuring contributions lead to real-world results.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1732147145548-0c245396a268?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxmZWF0dXJlZC1waG90b3MtZmVlZHwyMnx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
                alt="Transparency Builds Trust"
                class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Guidelines for Non-Profit Projects</h2>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Purpose-Driven Funding:</strong> Funds raised should
            directly support the non-profit initiative you've outlined. Every
            contribution should move your mission forward.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Ensure your project adheres to
            all legal requirements and regulations related to charitable
            fundraising within Thailand.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Optional Rewards:</strong> While offering rewards is not
            mandatory for non-profit projects, you may choose to provide updates
            or tokens of appreciation to acknowledge your supporters'
            generosity.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Begin Your Journey</a>
    </div>
</div>
